Release 0.2.0 - 2010-11-04 ----------------------------------------------------

* Second release of Rage, with the following features:
  . Background scrolling
  . Different background sizes (256x256 - 512x512)
  . Automatic palette handling


Release 0.1.2 - 2010-10-22 ----------------------------------------------------

* Bugfix for missing first frame of initial animation. Only showed up
  when the user didn't set the initial animation himself.


Release 0.1.1 - 2010-07-11 ----------------------------------------------------

* Bugfix for non-looping animations (showed index 0 after animation finished)
* Bugfix for displaying first frame of animation


Release 1 - 2010-07-01 --------------------------------------------------------

* First release of Rage, so that's the news for the day!
